43:33.446 --> 43:36.750
You know, there's still got to be in the public budget.

43:39.575 --> 43:41.337
It's in the budget.

43:41.357 --> 43:44.962
And just for the sake of the record, what's wrong with that?

43:45.844 --> 43:49.128
Well, I mean, a lot of things.

43:49.309 --> 43:54.476
First of all, it perverts what he wanted.

43:54.496 --> 43:55.858
You know, he wanted books.

43:56.395 --> 44:00.380
that there were no computers in there.

44:00.400 --> 44:04.785
I'm just playing devil's advocate.

44:05.446 --> 44:08.049
You're just asking me to articulate.

44:08.910 --> 44:10.812
Yes, I understand.

44:10.832 --> 44:11.613
Nothing bad at me.

44:11.633 --> 44:11.953
This is my joke.

44:11.973 --> 44:12.454
Right.

44:12.474 --> 44:26.250
